[size=20pt]FIRST OFF I CHANGED THE NAMES TO "Client" and if this stays on 1st page for a bit, might add open source.[/size]

Some Added items: DFS - 15186 Dark Bow - 15156 Summoning SC - 3630 Summoning Hood - 3632 D platebody - 8001 D kiteshield - 8001 D claws - 13610 Many more... just to lazy to put.
